Name: SMC
Title: BDD based symbolic model checker for the modal mu-calculus
Author: Kumar Neeraj Verma
Email: verma@lsv.ens-cachan.fr
Institution: LSV/Dyade/INRIA/IIT Delhi
Date: 2002-11
Description: Provides BDD algorithms, a symbolic model checker for the modal
             mu-calculus based on it, together with a garbage collector
Keywords: BDD, binary decision diagrams, classical logic, propositional logic,
          garbage collection, modal mu-calculus, model checking, symbolic model checking,
          reflection
Require: IntMap
Category: Computer Science/Decision Procedures and Certified Algorithms/Decision procedures
